Name: Hearty Stewmix Lv.2
Description: Recommended for Frost Mage, Verdant Oracle, and Soul Musician.
Description$english: Recommended for Frost Mage, Verdant Oracle, and Soul Musician.
Description2$english: A luxurious and complex dish with rich ingredients and intricate Artisanship. Its color, aroma, and taste are beyond words, and it often appears in various legends and stories. The most widely circulated tale is the (fictional) anecdote of a​ Seal Watcher gaining special powers after drinking this soup.

recipes.Name: Hearty Stewmix
recipes.Des:
Crafting yields products Lv.1, Lv.2, and Lv.3 at rates of 50%, 40%, and 10%, respectively.
An opulent masterpiece born of abundant ingredients and intricate craftsmanship—its vibrant hues, intoxicating aroma, and exquisite flavor merely herald what lies beyond. Revered in countless tales, this legendary dish is best known through the fictional account of a Seal Watcher who, upon sipping a single bowl, was granted supernatural powers.
